---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../consts";
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`Heat Repair Tupelo, MS | ${SITE.name}`}
  description="Need to fix heat in Tupelo? Review common no-heat symptoms, safe checks, and when to request heating repair."
  canonical={`${SITE.url}/heat-repair-tupelo/`}
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container surface service">
      <p class="eyebrow">Heat Repair Tupelo</p>
      <h1>Fix Heat Problems in Tupelo, MS</h1>
      <p>
        If your heating system runs without warming the home, cycles too often, or gives off unusual odors, request a
        heating diagnostic. North Mississippi cold snaps can expose weak igniters, airflow restrictions, and thermostat
        control issues.
      </p>
      <h2>Before calling a pro</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Set thermostat to heat mode and raise setpoint.</li>
        <li>Check and replace the air filter if dirty.</li>
        <li>Confirm power switches and breakers are on.</li>
        <li>Make sure supply registers are open.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        If your home still feels cold, request local heat repair. Also review
        <a href="/hvac-maintenance-tupelo/"> maintenance plans</a> to help prevent mid-season issues.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="button primary" href="/#request-service">Request Service</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">Get a Quote</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/tupelo-hvac-guide/">Read the Tupelo HVAC Guide</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .service {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 900px;
  }
  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
